Population = INTEG ( Births - Deaths, 1000 )
	~ Person
	~ 
	|
Births = Population * Birth Fraction
	~ Person/Month
	~ 
	|
Deaths = Population / Average Lifetime
	~ Person/Month
	~ 
	|
Birth Fraction = 0.02 * ( 1 - Crowding Effect )
	~ 1/Month
	~ 
	|
Average Lifetime = 75
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
Carrying Capacity = 5000
	~ Person
	~ 
	|
Crowding Effect = Population / Carrying Capacity
	~ Dmnl
	~ 
	|
INITIAL TIME = 0
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
FINAL TIME = 240
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
TIME STEP = 0.25
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
SAVEPER = TIME STEP
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
